{"tid":649882,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"冇圖 短文 500蚊鞋盒電腦 竟然玩到PUBG? 附懶人包","createTime":"2018-05-02T01:05:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T07:04:40.000Z","uid":131980,"like":372,"dislike":66,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"8d0144ac785719b0f7d5319db3bba3cb7ed60050","tid":649882,"uid":131980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T01:05:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">WARNING</span></strong>:<br />\n有時間就睇長文,無時間就睇懶人包,完.<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">懶人包</span></strong>:<br />\n起因-好奇500蚊食唔食到雞<br />\n經過-淘左一堆零件,但差個機箱,屋企又有個鞋盒,所以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果-拼埋一齊又開到機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,測試左3隻遊戲CSGO,LOL,PUBG.<br />\n-張&quot;顯卡&quot;差左o的<br />\n-勉強PUB到,但G就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n-CSGO,LOL PASS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<br />\n1慳位<br />\n2平<br />\n壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<br />\n1LOAD野好撚慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2PUBG睇o野好撚蒙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3個機箱一濕水就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">---完---</div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">長文慎閱,多圖慎看,驚你爆DATA</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n是咁的,話說最近小弟<br />\n1投資失利,買左利物浦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2生意失敗,學人炒黃牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3家破人亡,無撚左一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4比人呃錢,垃圾電視機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5撞撚左車,跟車太撚貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n  唉,實在太多不幸o事情發生o係我身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> .<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n  思想混亂.迷惘的我開始在商場漂蕩.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n  我停下來,閉起雙眼,聆聽四周,只有恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n此時醒起,屌,又肚餓喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後突然聞到由離我有50000毫米遠,來自蘇格蘭場非工業用國際線路自動溶雪16 Vallo 風油太垂直升降大包圍連擂射彩色洗衣乾衣腐蝕性氣墊專業急凍車運送到炸雞店炸炸雞的味道.那誘人的炸雞芬香<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,個個聞到都扯撚哂旗.此刻我知道,我只有一個目標,今!餐!要!食!雞!!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n  我便打開手上破爛的銀包,看見只剩下最後一張500蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再加50蚊飯錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我豪不猶疑地,去左香港某大型連鎖超級市場,買左個合味道,雞肉味,立即返屋企沖熱水解決左.<br />\n食到雪雪聲,Lamlam脷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.<br />\n<br />\n  不知不覺,每日o既生活都係咁過.......<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/065946_d37e1cf3fb878a6a3c7f3b5789a0d8c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F065946_d37e1cf3fb878a6a3c7f3b5789a0d8c5.jpg&h=1096b886&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">FORGET IT<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">畢氏池怡,開始上馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n提醒: MOON係 L豬 解析度係1366x768 <br />\nWHY?<br />\n1:隻144HZ 1080p 只支援 HDMI / DP ,我有DP線冇HDMI線<br />\n2:張卡只支援VGA,DVI,HDMI,冇DP所以<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次嘅菜色叫做北姑雞<br />\n材料有<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/070316_fa9aaad36e1b6499ad2537c181b71456.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F070316_fa9aaad36e1b6499ad2537c181b71456.jpg&h=a11a2680&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/075344_edbc24ce02cb7ddcedf19ce6e1c263db.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F075344_edbc24ce02cb7ddcedf19ce6e1c263db.png&h=c717e422&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nOKAY睇落無問題,即刻淘左佢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/075534_bfe5a5b3f527f2aac77ecd0ed67babf9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F075534_bfe5a5b3f527f2aac77ecd0ed67babf9.png&h=dce95b0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你無睇錯,係買左X5460,唔係E5450.點解?<br />\n詳請請睇:北上華強修理&quot;顯卡&quot;中伏遊當中o既支線任務<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/530391/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/530391/page/1</a><br />\n好,買齊喇,可以開始裝機Lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/075933_c41f10a9fe34e298f3b94e58bae658c7.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F075933_c41f10a9fe34e298f3b94e58bae658c7.jpeg&h=e4e72298&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌差個機箱.<br />\n突然間,我比硬物撞擊頭部,昏迷左0.1秒.<br />\n我起身後,發現左o的o野.E~,點解多左個鞋盒o既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n盒上寫住:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/081302_a760cb8507f0ff206d7aea61c91ed309.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F081302_a760cb8507f0ff206d7aea61c91ed309.png&h=26ddc0d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我同自己講<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/081441_11a4b04a110f7e9095f4340ca150146e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F081441_11a4b04a110f7e9095f4340ca150146e.jpg&h=91dfe015&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唉仲諗咩,無其他機箱可以頂檔,用住先啦!<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/081609_1469e337a1796ec421eacb700a7ac1ee.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F081609_1469e337a1796ec421eacb700a7ac1ee.jpeg&h=65f8562d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鞋盒其實同樓一樣,都係要有間隔.(全部都係實用面積!)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/081738_9a63dd7089e8597d2f49262fd796ddd9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F081738_9a63dd7089e8597d2f49262fd796ddd9.png&h=fd9400a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n裝裝下發現張卡頂撚住左,即刻剪撚左佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/081920_7180a8d3681caafd9a09317224894a08.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F081920_7180a8d3681caafd9a09317224894a08.jpeg&h=edd4eea1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搞掂食碗面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/083828_f00892dbae7abef402a0f44d18a575bf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F083828_f00892dbae7abef402a0f44d18a575bf.jpeg&h=0835fa1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/084313_5dbd133e18fe7db575a471d9c5cfe622.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F084313_5dbd133e18fe7db575a471d9c5cfe622.jpeg&h=3706feaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔好睇少紙皮,企直都唔會變形<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/082029_f3bba03647a75b6ab47dcfccbd177d78.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F082029_f3bba03647a75b6ab47dcfccbd177d78.jpeg&h=80bcb8e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/082043_b533036fde7fd7aac7e00f54cc859a78.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F082043_b533036fde7fd7aac7e00f54cc859a78.jpeg&h=9f8f7d83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nELEVATION,PLAN,END VIEW<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/082314_1608b453e0885630fd9ff7f45ad7229b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F082314_1608b453e0885630fd9ff7f45ad7229b.gif&h=94441c34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開蓋又得閂蓋都得,得左!<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/082345_a8819a7f4dd892e00780943778bdcfc1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F082345_a8819a7f4dd892e00780943778bdcfc1.jpeg&h=08b8f396&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n次次開機都咁撚樣,有無解決方法?我更新左BIOS一樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/082417_df6bb7d52160b98d6e675c9ffc998773.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F082417_df6bb7d52160b98d6e675c9ffc998773.jpeg&h=171f4d81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/082422_cde5604d35b3ad3168c61ab6ae62317a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F082422_cde5604d35b3ad3168c61ab6ae62317a.jpeg&h=969b0eab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n超一超先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBENCHMARK RESULT 係二樓<br />\n<br />\n總結:<br />\n鞋盒機箱唔難做,大家都做到,方便又環保(係用左好多索帶..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ),有蓋唔洗驚有太多塵,最怕濕姐.<br />\n最煩應該係剪箱,開洞,索部件.<br />\n散熱方面開蓋會減3度,可開可唔開.<br />\n<br />\n香港天氣潮濕咪仆街?電腦開機後有熱產生ga ma,渣ga<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,平衡左架喇,打和SUPER!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n張&quot;顯卡&quot;買返嚟勁撚臭,一聞到真係會狂咳同打黑痴.果隻味係大陸獨有o既網吧+煙味+冷氣機LOOP長年累月下而成,你老味2-3日開機轉風扇先散哂,on99<br />\n<br />\n其實我之前都有個紙做&quot;機箱&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/572932/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/572932/page/1</a><br />\n不過真係太樣衰,唔多想用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW:隔離個窮人水冷其實我之前都有諗過做,當時係打算用潛水泵加一大筒水,加冰,再駁2個水冷排,懶得做就告吹左,最大問題係唔夠位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下集預告/彩蛋<br />\n<br />\n壞件煮野食"},{"pid":"18f79db414b96d84be375c49508defaeb6426e2e","tid":649882,"uid":131980,"like":53,"dislike":7,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T01:06:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/083640_01dacd8b75e357f6e798b5340f526542.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F083640_01dacd8b75e357f6e798b5340f526542.jpeg&h=2a449bd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/082544_e9054f06ff98cb115d696546e89fe012.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F082544_e9054f06ff98cb115d696546e89fe012.jpeg&h=14ff0293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/082553_cbb443f01588b9d92f47a9500abb8b43.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F082553_cbb443f01588b9d92f47a9500abb8b43.jpeg&h=adaf5dba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLOL PASS!都叫穩定70FPS,打RANK走有o的危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\